Reasoning: The paper deals with graph width measures and their impact on the expressivity of CNF-formulas in the model of clausal encodings with auxiliary variables. This falls under the scope of theoretical computer science and specifically, the sub-categories of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), logic in computer science (cs.LO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
